                    {
                        "text": "Select \u201cTransfer of clinical responsibility\u201d. Select opinion only or Diagnostic test if this has been stated explicitly in the referral document."
                    },
                    {
                        "text": "Patient pathway identifier"
                    },
                    {
                        "text": "Defaults to \u201cRecord pathway manually\u201d - Leave as is."
                    },
                    {
