                    },
                    {
                        "text": "Click into this field and delete the Lorenzo generated PPI. Enter the Patient Pathway Identifier (PPI number) which will be on the MDS sheet. If the referral is still in the created state, this field will be blank, enter the Patient Pathway Identifier (PPID number) which will be on the MDS sheet."
                    },
                    {
                        "text": "Organisation involved in pathway"
                    },
                    {
                        "text": "Search & select referring organisation, click \u201cadd\u201d to add the referring organisation."
                    },
                    {
